žIn fond memory of
Our Founder Mrs June Mackay
Our Chairman John Perry
and Secretary Mrs Louise Perry (nee Conner)
from the members of the Brixton Dog Training Club"Č
ęFor Mary Crawford, Friend and CPG volunteer
She donated the grapefruit tree in the north corner
which was started from a pip in 1948
by her Aunt Queenie, Mrs EE Bell."«
źThis Bench was installed by Southwark Council in 2010
at the instigation of The Dulwich Society. It replaced the
original installed in memory of Bernard Webb (1934-2000)"╣
